  "title": "HR & Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>Job Scope:<br />--Process work pass applications, renewals, cancellations, and appeals (WP)<br />-Liaise with MOM and relevant authorities on work pass matters and regulatory requirements<br />-Stay updated on MOM policies, employment laws, and regulatory changes; provide timely updates to HR Manager and management<br />-Maintain and update employee records, contracts, and HR documentation<br />-Assist in onboarding and offboarding processes for local and foreign employees<br />-Support audits, inspections, and compliance checks related to MOM and employment regulations<br />-Handle general HR administrative tasks and ad-hoc duties as assigned<br /></p><p>Requirements:<br />-Must have at least 2years of experiences in HR Payroll system<br />-Familiar with MOM rules and regulations<br />- 5days work week<br /></p>",
